				<p class="news_content_date">2011-01-19</p>
				<h2>小六生必懂的十八趴威力--Passion: 慕容理深のblog</h2>
				<h4></h4>
                <div id="media_contents" class="w80 container">
	                					<hr>
	                <p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1 class="blogtitle" style="font-size: 1.34125em; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體; letter-spacing: 1px; "><a accesskey="1" class=" aptureTMMSelection" style="color: rgb(106, 108, 58); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; " target="_blank" href="http://blog.roodo.com/elysii/">Passion: 慕容理深のblog</a></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; ">【文章摘要】</p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">假設：</span></font><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; "><br />
</span></font></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">張三與李四在1989年年初各在台銀辦理10萬元定存；</span></font></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">兩筆存款年年到期自動續約至今；</span></font></p>
<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; ">
    <li><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">「一般人」張三以一年期固定利率定存；</span></font></li>
    <li><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">李四享有固定「十八趴」利率。</span></font></li>
</ul>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">在單利計算下，區區十萬元到了2011年年底，總共為張三帶來10萬6730元的利息，而李四得到的利息總額是41萬4000元。李四的獲利是張三的3.88倍。</span></font></p>
<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#111111" face="'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;如果李四當初存款金額是一百萬，那麼，他的獲利就是四百多萬。</span></font></p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 23px; ">以上道理淺顯，小六生必能懂，也必須懂，因為</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Lucida Grande', Georgia, serif, 新細明體; font-size: medium; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; ">目前當局仍處心積慮地恢復、維護的十八趴現在一年就需由全體納稅人支出 七、八百億來貼補。這項開銷不僅排擠眼前亟需挹注更多經費的教育、社福預算，也對近年來負債速度飆升的國家財政造成沈重的負擔。除非奇蹟發生，否則，現在的小學生、甚至猶在襁褓中的嬰兒，長大後都免不了被濫權妄增的公共債務本息壓到趴。我們這一代至今仍未能拆除黨國體系，而且還讓它全面復活肆虐，真是愧對國家未來的主人翁啊！</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
